{"tid":716011,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗奇蹟出線，葡萄牙爆冷出局，C朗緣盡世界杯，登機回程","createTime":"2018-06-25T02:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T10:00:11.000Z","uid":43785,"like":19,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2591521082480275c4fe35677acff04eb01d0a15","tid":716011,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T02:21:39.000Z","msg":"伊朗奇蹟出線，葡萄牙爆冷出局，C朗緣盡世界杯，登機回程<br />\n<br />\n上場伊朗既積極踢法搏盡掌聲，令王者西班牙毫無辦法。<br />\n今場面對後防較弱既葡萄牙隊，一定能突破重圍取得勝利出線。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙雖然有C朗拿度，但中後場鬆散如沙，面對本屆B組ATM摩洛哥，比伊朗踢得更差，亦不能佔上風，顯然爭杯無望。<br />\n<br />\n前兩場C朗一直踢一人足球，須要前中後場皆顧。已顯得十分吃力。<br />\n今仗敗給伊朗，與波蘭一起提早登機，未嘗不是一件好事。<br />\n否則下場面對烏拉圭及俄羅斯，也是毫無勝算。"},{"pid":"7b849d0a6a32ae07029631e944e3898e39e7ab29","tid":716011,"uid":9708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T02:23:41.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"c4678fadd88bfa5cb32ce37b0c8272c5f2d923e7","tid":716011,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T02:24:32.000Z","msg":"又燈"},{"pid":"69de6bdb5e0b0365dbad1112e007f8aac10c5e89","tid":716011,"uid":61211,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T02:26:09.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/portugal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9e4a1918b0e73b9679ef7d28491feae425f6fc","tid":716011,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T02:30:10.000Z","msg":"不安"},{"pid":"deff3c33795e53fa94f0609929c709fb8b412a2f","tid":716011,"uid":43785,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69de6bdb5e0b0365dbad1112e007f8aac10c5e89","tid":716011,"uid":61211,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T02:26:09.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/portugal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T02:36:42.000Z","msg":"支你老母，賤種朗出局"},{"pid":"b1362712b3441b6fba5740504fa50590bcfa4378","tid":716011,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T02:37:29.000Z","